{"tid":2202841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：消息指騰訊因中印美港局勢 正轉移陣地至星加坡","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T05:22:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"331f2a93f0602f8b0ffe05e6e79d85ca89923e3c","tid":2202841,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"報道指騰訊已選擇新加坡作為地區樞紐 <br />\n<br />\n彭博引述消息人士指，騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=67c3f0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)已選擇新加坡作為地區樞紐，並考慮將部分業務轉移至海外，包括國際遊戲發行，而近期中美及中印地緣政治升溫，正加快遷移業務計劃進展。 <br />\n<br />\n騰訊的聲明表示，除在馬來西亞、印尼及泰國外，將會在新加坡開設公司，支持正在增長的東南亞及以外地區業務，並聘請多項職位，包括科技及業務發展範疇。目前騰訊招聘頁面顯示，集團正在新加坡招聘跨境商貿、雲計算及電競相關職位。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2357222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2357222&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=013e1be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2357222</a>"},{"pid":"33e88307f96abdb605508b770c70cb6f40f8a130","tid":2202841,"uid":51271,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:32:38.000Z","msg":"你個名都臭晒啦，搬去邊都無用"},{"pid":"d057a00ccbf6589db3a53e4c15e37895d4fa6b18","tid":2202841,"uid":34065,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"人地係做鳩你支那國企 你總部唔係支那就唔做鳩你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0ff705c038f950abfcd2994129f32c6f917342","tid":2202841,"uid":267680,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"學海底撈走資 叻仔"},{"pid":"20d814e7e58a87d7069f30e0cdc013cc45b30648","tid":2202841,"uid":143499,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"243fe5946271107ed4d0dbd8ea37ced76ae754b3","tid":2202841,